text: Syosset is a hamlet and census-designated place (Syosset) in Nassau County, New York, United States, in the northeastern section of the Town of Oyster Bay, on the North Shore of Long Island. ==References== ==Other websites== * Syosset Chamber of Commerce Category:Hamlets in New York (state) Category:Census-designated places in New York (state)
title: Syosset, New York
